ActIndian Lands Agreement (1986) Act
PrecisConfirmation of a FINAL AGREEMENT between the BINGWI NEYAASHI ANISHINAABEK, the Crown and the Province of Ontario, which identifies some 984.603 hectares (2,433 acres) of land situated in the Territorial District of Thunder Bay, Geographic Township of Kilkenny at approximetaly 160 kilometres north east of the City of Thunder Bay, including all surface and subsurface rights, to be set apart as a reserve for the use and benefit of the Bingwi Neyaashi Anishinnabek (Sand Point First Nation). (LT-06-128)
